Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河的鬼斬役
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,末裔 可憎的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機…成熟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
